<p>UBC大学学费</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190916/03e2dbaece664257b78783e54497ef3a.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>应用科学专业，今年每个学分$1321.18，按照一年30学分计算，每年学费$39635.4。</p>
