<p>麦吉尔大学今年学费平均上涨3.6%</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190916/7c6085f47fbb4bc8b3239d429435e34e.JPG" max-width="600" /></p>
